title: Anjelah Johnson-Reyes
itunes:title: Anjelah Johnson-Reyes
description:
Comedian/actress/author Anjelah Johnson-Reyes (MADtv, ALVIN AND THE CHIPMUNKS, LOPEZ TONIGHT) is our guest this week and talks to Whitney about her time as a cheerleader in the NFL, taking acting classes from Jennifer Aniston and the cast of FRIENDS, and the dicks on the ceiling of the Sistine Chapel.  Anjelah's book WHO DO I THINK I AM? comes out on March 15, 2022.  

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
